g in a variety of courses history the hume writing center was founded in 2001 initially called the stanford writing center its name was changed to the hume writing center to honor the generous donation provided by george and leslie hume we provide over 6000 sessions of tutoring a year and provide consultations and workshops for graduate students in all seven graduate schools earth sciences education engineering humanities and sciences graduate school of business and medicine to get a brief summary of our history and our mission watch the youtube video of the two founding directors of the hume writing center you can also learn more about the hume writing center in the following articles stanford writing center praxis a writing center journal 4.1 fall 2006 web cynthia haven east palo alto high schoolers hone writing skills in campus program stanford report april 9 2008 web lindsay schauer giving project write gentry june 2008 142 hwc programs writing in the major introductory seminars honors writing and boot camp digital media consulting pwr stanford university 590 escondido mall stanford ca 94305 3069 650 723 2631 contact us terms of use copyright complaints site by wired moon
